  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium heat. Add the onion and garlic and sauté until softened. Add the eggplant and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally. Add the dashi extract, chili flakes, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine. Crumble in the Norwegian brown cheese and stir until melted. Remove from heat and stir in the feta cheese. Season with additional salt and pepper to taste. Garnish with fresh parsley."
